        <active>true</active>
        <article><![CDATA[<div>Configure which fields display on a form. You can hide and rearrange fields that agents do not often use to make the form more streamlined and usable.  Form layouts are configurable by views. Click <strong>Configure</strong> to learn more about Configuring a Form.</div>
<div><br /></div>
<div>Agent Workspace uses a hierarchy of views depending on the role of the agent and what views are available in the system.</div>
<ul style="list-style-position: inside;"><li>workspace_csm</li><li>workspace_itil</li><li>workspace</li></ul>
<p>If a workspace view is not configured, the system uses the default view in read-only and contains a message to contact the admin.</p>]]></article>
